name: Neotoma 1
notes:
Based on IntCal13 calibration curve. Set a 2-yr at hiatus at 20.5 cm to force the memory to zero to account for the post-Eurosettlement kink in accumulation rate.

Bacon command line:
Bacon('NEWARKVP',thick=5,acc.mean=c(10,50),hiatus.depths=20.5,hiatus.mean=2,depths.file=TRUE)

Bacon settings file:
0 #d.min
340.5 #d.max
1 #d.by
1 #depths.file
NA #slump
10 50 #acc.mean
1.5 1.5 #acc.shape
0.7 #mem.mean
4 #mem.strength
20.5 #hiatus.depths
2 #hiatus.mean
1 #hiatus.shape
0 #BCAD
1 #cc
0 #postbomb
IntCal13 #cc1
Marine13 #cc2
SHCal13 #cc3
ConstCal #cc4
cm #unit
0 #normal
3 #t.a
4 #t.b
0 #d.R
0 #d.STD
0.95 #prob
